            <div class="fs-18 fw-bold f-nunito text-red">
              Cross-border data transfers
            </div>
            <p>
              The DPDPA regulates the transfer of personal data to countries outside India. Organizations must ensure
              that adequate safeguards are in place to protect personal data when it is transferred to such countries.
            </p>
